Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------正片----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到换班时间了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一目标 镇压完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是相当无趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是「那个」圣地的警备吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是警备 不如说是用来监视牵制他国的摆设吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且换岗人员的生活设施 全都在圣地里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说只要潜入了内部 其余的就是小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本来应该是最困难的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉哟 第二、第三目标也镇压完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此下去 不就可以把全部的警备所都镇压了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也可以 但圣机师为数不多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要这么多茧也没用处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且被修利冯注意到就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.31,0:03:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的警备是完全独立的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来爱美拉去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种帮不上忙 又啰唆的人不在不是更好么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去处理我的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔父的走狗竟擅自使唤别人的属下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不晓礼数呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 那还真抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你这 看来很顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四、第五、第六目标 镇压完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 你就在一旁好好看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:41.75,*Default,STAFF,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45\fad(500,0)}校译：胖子 无尽空寂 始&终の零 润色：马甲雷 时间：Xelloss
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs120\fn方正粗宋_GBK\pos(960,780)\fad(500,0)\b0\fsp15\bord2\be1}袭 来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于今日的来临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人衷心致谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想并非空谈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动必得实施
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不失其意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位的各项努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将引领我们通往新生纪元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望诸位谨记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久后我军主力就会到达
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位出发吧 让此刻成为我们庆祝胜利的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警备所被…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得多赚点印象分才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利利索索地一个个收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们知道我们的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西会有用吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 如果离开水线会变回茧的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么声音啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪音？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯特雷尤正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:05:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸的浓烟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是警备所那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警备所？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么警报没有拉响？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地警备所 已排除近七成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 很不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在这里干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这究竟是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是让圣地由我支配而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯特雷尤的旗舰要塞！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个控制室也由我掌控了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部乖乖投降的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 那老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是这边 修利冯的圣机人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？藏了两台啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来解决 其他的交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 中央控制室被占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅斯特家的小鬼也摆出一幅自大的拽样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 知道了 马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为占领了那里就能支配一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人笑掉大牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那面具女说的风暴难道是指这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂止是风暴 简直是台风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的巴巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎样让巴比伦穿过那么狭窄的溪谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉夏拉陛下 学院长来电联络
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先能简洁说明一下目前所发生的状况吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也应该了解我在斯特雷尤的处境吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对天地神明发誓 这件事跟我毫无关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 现在的情况必须让全校人员去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能提供协助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用说吗?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学院长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 白鸟城立刻准备出发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去协助引导学生避难和抵御敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣地的教职人员已开始进行避难引导了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现今闯入圣地的可是斯特雷尤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在此时不做点事的话 我的立场就很不利了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家的训示是自己的事情自己做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你即使不肯替我出这个头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就权作是报答那些平日对你爱护有加的人也行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立刻就去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我走着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯雅 你也跟剑士一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然袭击我们的是斯特雷尤…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是达古麦亚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉夏拉陛下请尽快…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯雅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想和他一起的话 那就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是避难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七目标已攻陷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制室突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经足够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面差不多也乱作一团了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微去整点儿零用钱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦乌 瓦乌 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是外面好像很混乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个借我用用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？先别着急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的武器马上就装好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台足矣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东西装太多会影响机动力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据岚的情报 这里好像是圣机工的工房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没值钱的东西呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦乌 这家伙的反应变得更灵活了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来这些不都是之前偷袭保养地的山贼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦乌 这俩家伙交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～啊 等等 剑士 你要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥拉殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑精灵的负面时间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平常比起来真像完全变了个人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着这么害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会对你很温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:10:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐东西 那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你在抓着哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱动啊 要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宰了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点 就够着…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都让你看到我不成体统的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要没受伤就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负面时间真是可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再抱久一点也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是大好时机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个赶紧去确认是否有没来得及避难的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！电灯泡马上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑士阁下 公主就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 请一定努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这俩家伙 我要扣他们薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 实战起来貌似也没什么了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 真卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍伊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是反抗我们的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑精灵领域很麻烦 尽快解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙没有武装吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防卫机能启动了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们去确保避难学生的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰外各处中弹 但损伤轻微
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人炮台陆续出现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭他们已经做的很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让圣机人全体出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让这些家伙妨碍巴比伦的前进路线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴巴隆殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈伯尼瓦的芙罗拉女皇传来通信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴巴隆卿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对圣地进行军事侵犯 到底有何目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚问
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我你知道了来此处的理由又能怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想阻止我的话 就用实力来说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让我感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在圣地开战 若没有一些大义作口实可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴巴隆殿下 前方有巨大的物体靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全炮门展开完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射击开始～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 奉陪到底
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 真是好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是华丽的登场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也能接收避难学员与教职人员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请将通道打开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真帮了大忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 小心圣机人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边 请快些！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 好危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽缇亚会长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽缇亚会长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很危险 请别这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为大家争取点避难时间 我还能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双方数量太悬殊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 学生会长想登上圣机人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长阁下也想跟我们玩玩么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微吓吓她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:16:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽缇亚会长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个卑鄙小人不觉得羞耻吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许用那种臭屁的口气跟我们说话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉碧丝快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 我要保护丽缇亚会长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈 自己找死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.07,0:17:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剑士 那个碍眼的侍从
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 拉碧丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 丽缇亚会长没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 快起来 抓住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭了 拉碧丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会痛扁他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥拉殿下 这台机工人交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里？ 野生动物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙落荒而逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗技场的防御体系相当健全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣机人越不过埃纳的水线 这里很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各班长确认人员的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:19:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1班到4班从地下16号通道搭乘教会战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5班到8班从29号通道前往拉夏拉陛下的白鸟城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9班以后从7号通道进入芙罗拉陛下的装甲列车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清楚各自去向就开始避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那按照学号排列好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾诺跟布露是8 耶丽丝拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的吧 达古麦亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道总有一天会变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塞亚老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是拉夏拉陛下的护卫骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他是梅斯特家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塞亚老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各班级全部到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家按顺序兵分三路经地下通道避难了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个也快去避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 剑士小弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑士小弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想干什么啊？ 那个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被大家稍微捧高些就自以为了不起似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但毕竟只是个侍从
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂能与我们男性圣机师相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 打中了 打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本区域没落下什么人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人真够呛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在圣地开着装甲列车和战舰火拼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.11,0:21:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是前所未闻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达古麦亚殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.75,0:21:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是 剑士先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他究竟想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 那家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:21:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑士同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.49,0:22:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.76,0:22:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学员和职员总计1149人 均于白鸟城得到妥善保护
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.40,0:22:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人员健康状态良好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.76,0:22:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负伤者也仅为轻伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.37,0:22:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.66,0:22:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若就此让两人一同见鬼去就谢天谢地了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.65,0:22:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两方都活力十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.88,0:22:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然都怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:22:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑士君？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.94,0:23:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉夏拉陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.00,0:23:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.62,0:23:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.07,0:23:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 那是光之属性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.06,0:23:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光之属性？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.02,0:23:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教会秘藏的古代文献中曾提到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.81,0:23:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为光所笼罩之人拯救世界 为暗所笼罩之人毁灭世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:23:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为暗…所笼罩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.59,0:24:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是光与暗表里一体
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.40,0:24:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光或许会转为暗 反之亦然
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.31,0:24:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是白色的圣机人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.78,0:24:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那时的圣机人驾驶员是剑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.34,0:24:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣机师？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.02,0:24:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是我们的剑士吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.82,0:24:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 才一转眼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.79,0:24:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊 谁来救救我啊啊啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.70,0:25:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 不要背对着那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.94,0:25:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 从我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.25,0:25:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.91,0:25:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达古麦亚殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.72,0:25:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.19,0:25:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦乌安丽 去掩护他
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.82,0:25:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在没那个空闲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.45,0:25:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货 正中下怀 收拾掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.77,0:26:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 在那里面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.84,0:26:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一对一倒也罢了 以寡敌众的话可十分不利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.29,0:26:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是被石柱和埃纳水线环绕的牢笼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.38,0:26:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑士小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.46,0:26:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.17,0:26:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塞亚姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.38,0:26:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这林立的石柱里 机动力无法得到发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.94,0:26:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.40,0:26:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.45,0:26:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.14,0:26:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从左右迂回包抄
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.76,0:26:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.63,0:27:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往你的方向去了 柯露蒂涅
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.40,0:27:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 来吧 老娘会好好疼爱你的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.03,0:27:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在这里起跳
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.38,0:27:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.80,0:27:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.17,0:27:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.80,0:27:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊？那个圣机人的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.27,0:27:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没见过纯白的圣机人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.32,0:28:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.13,0:28:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是我们的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.93,0:28:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柾木剑士同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.37,0:28:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 剑士同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.97,0:28:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉夏拉陛下的随从？ 他是圣机师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.01,0:28:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上茧时 是我亲眼所见的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.64,0:28:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说那白色圣机人是剑士在驾驶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.35,0:28:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 剑士小弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.85,0:28:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.27,0:28:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是剑士同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.25,0:28:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个柾木剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.19,0:28:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.07,0:28:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在林立的石柱与水线的环绕下战斗极为困难
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.44,0:28:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.37,0:28:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真有那么难吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.67,0:28:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傻小子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.30,0:28:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.27,0:28:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽有众多已至达人境界的圣机师们在此斗技场中战斗过
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.79,0:28:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还没有谁能完成那样的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.04,0:28:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超乎想像啊 那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.33,0:29:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达古麦亚 此时应选择暂时撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.20,0:29:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说什么 怎能因为那家伙而退兵
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.35,0:29:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.60,0:29:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.90,0:29:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里夫
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.04,0:29:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.26,0:29:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒是我们自投罗网 被诱入了他的狩猎场吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.90,0:30:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后大人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.80,0:30:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了 雪音妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.89,0:30:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你保护玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.57,0:30:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂敢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.36,0:30:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来吃惊的事还真多
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.12,0:30:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到剑士是圣机师
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.37,0:30:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.32,0:30:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.30,0:30:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还拥有那么强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.43,0:30:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次可要找拉夏拉好好地询问清楚才行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.39,0:30:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.48,0:30:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了剑士 敌人的圣机人近乎全军覆没
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.45,0:30:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应可迫使斯特雷尤就此撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.14,0:30:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真不好说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.60,0:30:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.63,0:30:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎还备有后手呢 巴巴隆卿
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.42,0:30:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.97,0:30:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴比伦 到达目标
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.77,0:30:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰身控制 误差修正
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.76,0:31:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结界确认 构造检查 扫描开始
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.69,0:31:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反结界阵 开始构筑
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.63,0:31:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.05,0:31:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道巴巴隆的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.99,0:31:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.26,0:31:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}为什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.98,0:31:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达古麦亚
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.61,0:31:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.59,0:31:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 柯露蒂涅还…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.29,0:31:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈的话她自己会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.06,0:32:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这种怪物我能有什么办法啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.62,0:32:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 梅塞亚姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.49,0:32:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 难道你听不见我的声音吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.37,0:32:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.22,0:32:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违了 凯亚
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.69,0:32:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.57,0:32:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.89,0:32:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快你就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.04,0:32:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.02,0:32:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣机神的台座…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.08,0:32:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塞亚姐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.86,0:32:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.04,0:32:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结界解析完成 开始侵入
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.73,0:33:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.22,0:33:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.87,0:33:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 觉醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.80,0:33:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.20,0:33:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯亚 梅塞亚其实并非你的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.40,0:33:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塞亚是你父亲在遗迹中与圣机神一同被发掘出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.56,0:33:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先史文明所创造出来的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.78,0:33:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.46,0:33:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.47,0:33:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.11,0:34:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多…露…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.10,0:34:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.20,0:34:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.57,0:34:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接通教皇陛下的直通专线
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.69,0:34:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟有此事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.32,0:34:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万分之一机率的事态被触发了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.79,0:34:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴虐之神的复活！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.60,0:34:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.99,0:35:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快带领大家去避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.93,0:35:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想让她们陪葬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.92,0:35:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 梅塞亚姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.53,0:35:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.01,0:35:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.81,0:35:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.52,0:35:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 仅靠圣机人就有这能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.07,0:35:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很危险 快去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.88,0:36:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做好最后的确认后也会离开
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.64,0:36:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能留下你在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.60,0:36:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能丢下那个傻小子和姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.66,0:36:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你一定要平安归来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.98,0:36:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 这样就结束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.95,0:36:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔？怎么了？攻击啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.28,0:36:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么对剑士下不了手呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.77,0:36:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受梅塞亚的人格影响？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.11,0:36:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.31,0:36:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我不能拒绝命令
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.58,0:36:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.80,0:36:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细胞组织的劣化似乎比预想的还要糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.06,0:36:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯雅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.07,0:36:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有落单的学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.57,0:36:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也差不多该去避难了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.08,0:36:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是剑士先生还…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.33,0:36:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经没什么能做的了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.60,0:37:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扰敌之类的工作还能做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.23,0:37:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 被对方当成目标会很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.68,0:37:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我们很可能会拖剑士的后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.38,0:37:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退吧 那白痴的话没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.19,0:37:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.00,0:37:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.67,0:37:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒吧 梅塞亚姐
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.48,0:37:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.07,0:37:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塞亚跟我已经融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.13,0:37:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我记得 在这里和你一同经历过的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.48,0:37:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五花八门的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.58,0:37:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 你能把那些忘掉就感激不尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.91,0:37:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然的确是很愉快的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.00,0:37:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我已无法继续待在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.04,0:37:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 剑士 能到我的身边来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.31,0:37:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里没有我的容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.92,0:38:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒是多露 来我们这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.55,0:38:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的容身之所我会帮你开拓的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.24,0:38:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.70,0:38:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.56,0:38:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗才是我存在的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.61,0:38:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为此而被制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.59,0:38:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样就满足了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.71,0:38:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.09,0:38:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑士…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.92,0:38:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学院长 已确认全部学生避难完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.15,0:38:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那么准备出发
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.51,0:38:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.94,0:38:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没事吗？ 奥拉殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.18,0:38:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损害状况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.56,0:38:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了剑士阁下 全都获救了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.41,0:38:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那么立刻出航
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.55,0:38:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙罗拉陛下 来列车避难的学生已全部收容完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.80,0:38:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽有数人受伤 但221人均平安抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.31,0:38:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.30,0:39:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.53,0:39:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后大人 剑士先生还在战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.31,0:39:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 但应该不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.75,0:39:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 雪音妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.84,0:39:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮发射准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.92,0:39:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员撤退完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.09,0:39:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指挥车辆撤退到安全区域
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.60,0:39:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮发射后让前方车辆自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.93,0:39:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切顺利的话应该能阻止敌人追击哦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.74,0:39:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塞亚姐
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.55,0:39:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.95,0:39:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.77,0:39:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.16,0:39:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我母后现在要做蠢事了 请回避！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.12,0:39:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.17,0:40:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.26,0:40:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.38,0:40:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塞亚姐
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.00,0:40:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是无计可施啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.06,0:40:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想夺回圣地 我们连像样的战斗力都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.38,0:40:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么去结界工房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.71,0:40:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.78,0:40:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果万一圣机神启动的话 就来我这里 」
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.97,0:40:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈瓦师傅这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.85,0:40:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.47,0:41:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚯嚯
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.71,0:41:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差不多该把你知道的全都说出来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.12,0:41:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.12,0:41:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那里之前
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.56,0:41:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑士 去迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.52,0:41:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.30,0:41:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织严重劣化 剑士的力量太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.50,0:41:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还能战斗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.84,0:41:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连变型都没戏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.02,0:41:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.64,0:41:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.88,0:41:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.70,0:41:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙罗拉你个大姨妈
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.26,0:41:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个没常识的中年女人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.32,0:41:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们都卷进去的话可怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.00,0:41:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正得救了 就随她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.84,0:41:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果OK怎样都行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.65,0:42:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.15,0:42:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易收集的水晶全都落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.44,0:42:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～费了好大的功夫的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.85,0:42:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.93,0:42:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的确已约法三章不许再挖水晶的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.76,0:42:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这事 必须给我老实交代！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.46,0:42:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.78,0:42:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没危机感的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.93,0:42:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达古麦亚 作战是成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.27,0:42:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无须如此沮丧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.59,0:42:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.36,0:42:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太勉强自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.60,0:42:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次我可不一定在你身边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.92,0:43:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.88,0:43:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟预期一样潜伏其中
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.53,0:43:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的准备也很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.35,0:43:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------Destino--------------------------
